Title: What is OpenAI's new Agent Kit? (a quick guide)
Description:
OpenAI has just introduced Agent Kit, a complete set of tools to help you move AI agents from prototype to production. This quick overview covers the three main components: Agent Builder for visual workflows, a Connector Registry for secure APIs, and the embeddable Chat Kit UI for deployment.
